General.Name: Embark Early Education Limited
General.Description: Embark Early Education Limited provides early childhood education and care services in Australia. The company operates and manages ECE centers under the Roseberry House, Brighthouse, Cubby Care, HAVEN Early Learning, Kitiwah Place, Little Zebra, Carlton House, Moreton Drive Early Learning Centre, and Youngstars brand names. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Helensvale, Australia.
